  "textPreview": "Free June 9 event: How to win brand visibility when AI decides what gets seen →\nHelp Center\nRequest a demo\nStand with Ukraine\nWhy SE Ranking\nFeatures\nPlans & pricing\nResources\nSign up for free courses\nSE Ranking Academy\n\nDiscover proven strategies and tips with SE Ranking’s tutorials and courses, tailored to help you get more traffic and stand out in search. Start learning now — free for paid and trial users.\n\nStart learning today\nExpand your SEO expertise with SE Ranking\nFEATURED COURSE\nCertificate\n21 lessons\n2 hours\nKick things off with the Getting Started with SE Ranking course\n \n \n \n0:56\n \nStart learning\nEXPERT-LED COURSE\nRegularly updated\n5 lessons\n1 hour\nTap into AI-powered ranking wins with AI for SEO: Expert Framework\nStart learning\nNEW OPPORTUNITY FOR AGENCIES!\n60 questions\n2 hours\nGet SE Ranking certified to boost your credibility\nGet started\nAll courses and workshops\nAll courses\nSE Ranking Expertise\nSEO Mastery\nSEO Trends\nCertificate\n21 Lessons\n2 hours\nGetting Started with SE Ranking\nDiscover SE Ranking's core tools and features in this beginner-friendly course designed to help you kickstart your SEO success.\nStart course\nCertificate\nBadge\n2 hours\nSE Ranking Certification Exam\nTest your expertise and demonstrate your ability to leverage SE Ranking's tools to achieve results in SEO and digital marketing.\nGet certified\nCertificate\n6 Lessons\nAI Search: Understanding and tracking visibility with SE Ranking’s toolkit\nLearn how to confidently use AI search insights and SE Ranking’s AI Search Toolkit to speed up keyword research, competitive analysis, and content optimization.\nStart course\n8 Lessons\n2 hours\nAI for SEO: Expert Framework\nLearn how to streamline your SEO workflow with AI—from content creation to optimization and strategy—guided by real-world experts.\nStart course\n8 Lessons\n4+ hours\nSEO Foresight 2025: LLM’s Impact, Google's AI Updates, and Content Trends\nFind out what’s ahead for SEO and digital marketing in 2025 with insights from industry leaders",
